title: 2020 Isn't Over Yet
itunes:title: 2020 Isn't Over Yet
description:
So many of you have given up on 2020. I see it all over social media. People are wishing 2020 was over.
 
Today I tell you why this wish is not helpful to you or to your weightloss. Wishing away time and giving up on yourself and what's happening around you is not a great way to make your goals.
 
In this episode I help you see your thinking around Covid and 2020 and help you work on a change that will feel so much better.
 
Get the Free Course here:
http://phit.click/freecourse
